  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      patients with resistant hypertension will be submitted to an exercise protocol in a heated
      pool for three months
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      pacient´s blood pressure behavior will be compared before and after intervention
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
