  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with uncontrolled blood pressure despite concurrent use of 3 antihypertensive
             agents, including a diuretic, or the need for more than 3 medications to control blood
             pressure

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  poor adherence to the treatment

          -  obesity

          -  diabetes

          -  smokers

          -  secondary causes of hypertension

          -  motor disabilities to perform the training
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
